    "#data model making start ------main work start from here"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 74,
   "id": "545ca745-fd88-43a5-bbc7-1f9c74d52710",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from nltk.corpus import stopwords\n",
    "from nltk.stem.porter import PorterStemmer as ps\n",
    "def tft(tx):\n",
    "    tx = tx.lower()\n",
    "    tx = nltk.word_tokenize(tx)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    y = []\n",
    "    for i in tx:\n",
    "        if i.isalnum():\n",
    "            y.append(i)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    tx = y[:]\n",
    "    y.clear()\n",
    "    \n",
    "    for i in tx:\n",
    "        if i not in stopwords.words('english') and i not in string.punctuation:\n",
    "            y.append(i)\n",
    "            \n",
    "    tx = y[:]\n",
    "    y.clear()\n",
    "    stemmer = ps()\n",
    "    for i in tx:\n",
    "        y.append(stemmer.stem(i))\n",
    "    \n",
    "            \n",
    "    return \" \".join(y)"
   ]
  },

   "source": [
    "clfs = {\n",
    "    'SVC' : svc,\n",
    "    'AdaBoost': abc, \n",
    "    'BgC': bc, \n",
    "    'ETC': etc,\n",
    "    'GBDT':gbdt,\n",
    "    'xgb':xgb,\n",
    "    'KN' : knc, \n",
    "    'NB': mnb, \n",
    "    'DT': dtc, \n",
    "    'LR': lrc, \n",
    "    'RF': rfc, \n",
    "    \n",
    "}\n",
    "     "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 87,
   "id": "110ba0cf-c81b-4f9a-9502-edf4a1bb86c5",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def traindata(clf,X_train,y_train,X_test,y_test):\n",
    "    clf.fit(X_train,y_train)\n",
    "    y_pred = clf.predict(X_test)\n",
    "    accuracy = accuracy_score(y_test,y_pred)\n",
    "    precision = precision_score(y_test,y_pred)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return accuracy,precision"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 88,
   "id": "cb46a050-cb02-4a07-9090-75dda98ff161",

   "source": [
    "accuracy_scores = []\n",
    "precision_scores = []\n",
    "for name,clf in clfs.items():\n",
    "    \n",
    "    current_accuracy,current_precision = traindata(clf, X_train,y_train,X_test,y_test)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    print(\"For \",name)\n",
    "    print(\"Accuracy - \",current_accuracy)\n",
    "    print(\"Precision - \",current_precision)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    accuracy_scores.append(current_accuracy)\n",
    "    precision_scores.append(current_precision)\n",
    "     "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 91,
   "id": "a799dbe0-eae0-410a-83a4-383280d1f4fb",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "performance_df = pd.DataFrame({'Algorithm':clfs.keys(),'Accuracy':accuracy_scores,'Precision':precision_scores}).sort_values('Precision',ascending=False)\n",
    "     "
   ]

   "source": [
    "def classify_email(email):\n",
    "    transformed_email = tft(email)\n",
    "    X_email = tfidf.transform([transformed_email]).toarray()\n",
    "    prediction = mnb.predict(X_email)\n",
    "    if prediction[0] == 1:\n",
    "        return \"Spam/fraud massage\"\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        return \"Not Spam massage\""
   ]
  },
